# Plugin capacitor-thermal-printer (peer @capacitor/core ^7) dipakai di Capacitor 8.
# Native-nya terbukti kompatibel & build APK hijau, tapi npm ci (Cloudflare Pages)
# strict → ERESOLVE. legacy-peer-deps melonggarkan cek peer agar install lolos
